headline: How Tariffs Could Shock America’s Power System
summary: America’s power grid is due for some big investments.  Tariffs could now make that much costlier.  As surging power demand from places such as data centers is set to strain the system, transformers, the nuts and bolts of the power system, look particularly vulnerable.
